f-us-part-2-exclusive-interview-neil-druckmann-ellie/ |title=The Last of Us Part 2 exclusive interview: Neil Druckmann on Ellie sexuality, video game violence and the 'death' of Joel |last=Silver |first=Dan |work=[[Daily Telegraph|The Telegraph]] |publisher=[[Telegraph Media Group]] |date=September 26, 2019 |accessdate=September 26, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926152637/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/gaming/features/the-last-of-us-part-2-exclusive-interview-neil-druckmann-ellie/ |archivedate=September 26, 2019 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"USgamer Final Scene\">{{cite web |url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-last-of-us-part-2-finished-shooting-its-final-scene |title=The Last of Us Part 2 Has Finished Shooting Its Final Scene |last=Kim |first=Matt |work=[[USGamer]] |publisher=[[Gamer Network]] |date=April 17, 2019 |accessdate=May 8, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508131046/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/the-last-of-us-part-2-finished-shooting-its-final-scene |archivedate=May 8, 2019 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VentureBeat Directors\">{{cite web |url=https://venturebeat.com/2018/06/14/the-last-of-us-part-ii-game-directors-unravel-their-e3-demo-for-us/ |title=The Last of Us Part II game directors unravel their E3 demo for us |last=Takahashi |first=Dean |website=[[VentureBeat]] |date=June 14, 2018 |accessdate=October 24, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180614155327/https://venturebeat.com/2018/06/14/the-last-of-us-part-ii-game-directors-unravel-their-e3-demo-for-us/ |archivedate=June 14, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Wells Update\">{{cite web |url=https://www.naughtydog.com/blog/studio_update_neil_druckmann_the_last_of_us_part_ii |title=An Update from Studio President Evan Wells |last=Wells |first=Evan |authorlink=Evan Wells |work=[[Naughty Dog]] |publisher=[[Sony Interactive Entertainment]] |date=March 9, 2018 |accessdate=March 10, 2018 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation