I delayed indefinitely due to novel coronavirus|last=Peters|first=Jay|date=April 2, 2020|website=[[The Verge]]|publisher=[[Vox Media]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402193302/https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/2/21205819/sony-the-last-of-us-part-ii-delayed-indefinitely-coronavirus-iron-man-vr|archive-date=April 2, 2020|access-date=April 2, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Reception -->\n\n<ref name=\"Engadget Gameplay\">{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2018/06/11/the-last-of-us-part-ii-first-gameplay-footage/ |title=First 'The Last of Us: Part II' gameplay shows off refined combat |last=Ingraham |first=Nathan |work=[[Engadget]] |publisher=[[Verizon Media]] |date=June 11, 2018 |accessdate=October 24, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612182412/https://www.engadget.com/2018/06/11/the-last-of-us-part-ii-first-gameplay-footage/ |archivedate=June 12, 2018 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Game Awards 2017\">{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2017-winners-headlined-by-zelda-br/1100-6455467/ |title=The Game Awards 2017 Winners Headlined By Zelda: Breath Of The Wild's Game Of The Year |last=Makuch |first=Eddie |work=[[GameSpot]] |publisher=[[CBS Interactive]] |date=December 8, 2017 |accessdate=October 7, 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171209043912/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-game-awards-2017-winners-headlined-by-zelda-br/1100-6455467/ |archivedate=December 9, 2017 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Game Critics 2018\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/news/402511-playstation-and-ps4-won-e3-2018-according-to-game-critics-awards |title=PlayStation and PS4 Won E3 2018, According to Game Critics Awards |last=Ashaari |first=Alleef |work=[[Game Revolution]] |publisher=[[CraveOnline]] |date=July 2, 2018 |accessdate=July 4, 2018 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708052055/http://www.gamerevolution.com/news/402511-playstation-and-ps4-won-e3-2018-accord