f 1\">{{Cite web|url=https://kotaku.com/the-last-of-us-ii-delayed-indefinitely-1842646231?rev=1585850473534|title=The Last of Us II Delayed Indefinitely|last=Schreier|first=Jason|date=April 2, 2020|website=[[Kotaku]]|publisher=[[G/O Media]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402193253/https://kotaku.com/the-last-of-us-ii-delayed-indefinitely-1842646231?rev=1585850473534|archive-date=April 2, 2020|access-date=April 2, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Delay Indef 2\">{{Cite web|url=https://uk.ign.com/articles/the-last-of-us-part-2-delayed-indefinitely-no-new-release-date-set|title=The Last of Us Part 2 Delayed Indefinitely, No New Release Date Set|last=Dornbush|first=Jonathon|date=April 2, 2020|website=[[IGN]]|publisher=[[Ziff Davis]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402193452/https://uk.ign.com/articles/the-last-of-us-part-2-delayed-indefinitely-no-new-release-date-set|archive-date=April 2, 2020|access-date=April 2, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Delay Indef 3\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/2/21205819/sony-the-last-of-us-part-ii-delayed-indefinitely-coronavirus-iron-man-vr|title=The Last of Us Part II delayed indefinitely due to novel coronavirus|last=Peters|first=Jay|date=April 2, 2020|website=[[The Verge]]|publisher=[[Vox Media]]|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200402193302/https://www.theverge.com/2020/4/2/21205819/sony-the-last-of-us-part-ii-delayed-indefinitely-coronavirus-iron-man-vr|archive-date=April 2, 2020|access-date=April 2, 2020}}</ref>\n\n<!-- Reception -->\n\n<ref name=\"Engadget Gameplay\">{{cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2018/06/11/the-last-of-us-part-ii-first-gameplay-footage/ |title=First 'The Last of Us: Part II' gameplay shows off refined combat |last=Ingraham |first=Nathan |work=[[Engadget]] |publisher=[[Verizon Media]] |date=June 11, 2018 |accessdate=October 24, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612182412/https://www.engadget.com/20